# Casual Slides — web app build-time env. Copy to `.env` (or `.env.local`
# for personal overrides) and adjust. Vite inlines `VITE_*` values into
# the bundle at build time.

# Enable real-time collab. Default: disabled.
#
# When 'true', CollabProvider honours the `?room=…` URL param and opens
# the Hocuspocus / raw-WS bridge. Several editing paths still bypass the
# command bus (drag-reorder, theme cascade, find-replace, format pane,
# layout, background, slide context moves) and would silently desync
# concurrent edits in a shared room — opt in only when you've patched
# fork-side `slide.mutation.*` (UNIVER_SLIDES_GAPS.md Gap 1.4).
#
# VITE_COLLAB_ENABLED=true
